debrief.itemText: Please answer the following questions about your experience. Click and drag the red scrollbar to move down. Do not leave any box blank. Type ‘no’ or ‘n/a’ if you don’t have a response.
Briefly describe what you were asked to do in this experiment? (if there is existing text in the box delete it.
debrief.response: I was asked to look shapes that was represented by a number or letter. The shape was shown then the number and letter where shown. I was ask to click certain keys if the number was above or below 153 and if the letter was closer to A or Z. I had a set amount of time to do this and it got faster as the trial went on.
